OL,3,CThe moving story behind these stunning
OL,4,Cflowers at Cardiff Castle
OL,6,FA spectacular display of metal roses
OL,7,Fis captivating visitors to Cardiff
OL,8,FCastle, part of a campaign to raise
OL,9,Fmoney for the City Hospice.
OL,11,FThe 'Remember Me Roses' are intended
OL,12,Ffor people to buy to help remember a
OL,13,Ffamily member or friend.
OL,15,FThe individual roses combine to form
OL,16,Fpart of the display on the castle's
OL,17,Fbanks, before owners can take them
OL,18,Faway to keep at a place of their
OL,19,Fchoosing.
