OL,3,CThe moving story behind these stunning
OL,4,Cflowers at Cardiff Castle
OL,6,FNow back for the fourth year, the
OL,7,Fproject was launched during the
OL,8,Fpandemic as a way of helping people
OL,9,Fmark a loved one's passing at a time
OL,10,Fwhere funerals and end of life visits
OL,11,Fwere held under very restricted
OL,12,Fcircumstances.
OL,14,F"We came up with the concept of
OL,15,FForever Flowers as something that was
OL,16,Fquite meaningful and special" says
OL,17,FCity Hospice Chief Executive Liz
OL,18,FBooyse.
