OL,3,CThe moving story behind these stunning
OL,4,Cflowers at Cardiff Castle
OL,6,F"We have a wonderful community in
OL,7,FCardiff where people want to support
OL,8,Ftheir local hospice. This is an
OL,9,Fopportunity for them to do so, but
OL,10,Falso to come together as a community
OL,11,Fand remember loved ones."
OL,13,FThe charity provides palliative care
OL,14,Fto patients in their own homes, along
OL,15,Fwith counselling support for their
OL,16,Ffamilies, and is celebrating its 40th
OL,17,Fanniversary this year.
OL,19,FThe display will be at the Castle
OL,20,Funtil August 11.
